                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.1828/5: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Costa Rica</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-03-31T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 31, 1923—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>10. Legation’s no. 19. This Government would be pleased to have canal protocol
                    ratified but you should not make any representations to secure action to that
                    end.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
